# windows-path-adder

open cmd in windows
```bat
echo %PATH%
:: C:\foo;D:\boo

python -m windowspathadder "D:/new/path"
:: or python -m windowspathadder "D:\new\path"

echo %PATH%
:: D:\new\path;C:\foo;D:\boo

:: the previous path is backed up with timestamp.
echo %PATH_{timestamp}%
:: C:\foo;D:\boo
```

